<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kumsul vei ta ka nun lui leh hun pha,
 Malai suok ding nei ta maw?
 Bangkim gel khawmin,
 Suihlung na suhel ngei!

[V2]
 Ka ngilh lah, ka ngilh lah,
 Aw, hun leh kumlui muolliem;
 Na sungah chitin namtin ka lengkhawm ui,
 Chang bang dama kawp bang kim lai kha.

[V3]
 2. Nunnuom kawlni a kiem, Aw mi zapi,
 Nunnuom pak hawih a tuoi tai;
 Namtin hin hun chieh nung,
 Ngaiin I thil zing ui.

[V4]
 3. Thei mai leng chuh ninnuom kawlni tu'ng ka,
 Zamuolpi a liem mai tai;
 Nunlui ngaiin ka mau,
 Nunnuom a ka lennau.

[V5]
 4. Kum lui zamuol liem nung sapkit theih loh,
 Guoldeih gibang khensate;
 A hinkhuou buting in,
 Hun in a liempih tai.</lyrics>
<title>HOW DEPLORABLE THOU ART...!</title>
</song>